"      Sutton C, Minelli L, Garcia E, et al, &ldquo;Use of Icodextrin 4% Solution in the Reduction of Adhesion Formation After Gynaecological Surgery,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       Gynecol Surg",
"      </i>",
"      , 2005, 2(4): 287-296.",
